high_descs: Move forward then left and then right to be in front of the tv.
Pick up the figurine sitting on the bottom left of the table.
Turn right and then right again to  Face the coffee table.
Place the figurine on the bottom right of the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the figurine to the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk straight and get to the other side of the table, facing the statue
Grab the statue on the table
Turn around and walk to the coffee table
Put the statue on the right bottom corner of the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Move the statue on the table to the corner of the coffee table

high_descs: Walk straight ahead to the wooden table in front of you, then walk left then right and turn so you're facing the television screen
Pick up the statue on the table in front of you
Turn 180 degrees and walk towards the sofa, then turn right and see the small wooden table
Place the statue on the short wooden table
anns.task_desc: Pick up a small statue from the tv stand and place it on the wooden table
